<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Novus - 혁신적인 협업 툴</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;800&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            brand: '#6366f1',
            dark: '#0f172a',
            surface: '#1e293b',
          },
          fontFamily: {
            display: ['Inter', 'sans-serif'],
            sans: ['Noto Sans KR', 'sans-serif'],
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-dark text-gray-300 font-sans antialiased">

  <!-- Nav -->
  <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 backdrop-blur-lg border-b border-white/10">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 font-display font-bold text-white text-xl">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-brand rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">N</div>
        Novus
      </div>
      <div class="hidden md:flex gap-8 text-sm font-medium">
        <a href="#features" class="hover:text-white transition">기능 소개</a>
        <a href="#pricing" class="hover:text-white transition">요금제</a>
        <a href="#blog" class="hover:text-white transition">블로그</a>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <button class="hidden md:block text-sm font-bold text-white hover:text-brand transition">로그인</button>
        <button onclick="toggleNovus()" class="bg-brand text-white px-5 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold hover:bg-brand/90 transition shadow-lg shadow-brand/25">
          무료로 시작하기
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <header class="pt-40 pb-20 px-6 container mx-auto text-center relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background Glows -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[800px] h-[500px] bg-brand/20 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10"></div>
    
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-8 animate-fade-in-up">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-surface border border-white/10 rounded-full px-4 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-brand">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand animate-pulse"></span>
        v2.0 업데이트 출시
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-display font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">
        팀워크의 새로운 기준, <br>
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-brand to-purple-500">Novus</span>로 완성하세요.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        복잡한 프로젝트 관리부터 실시간 커뮤니케이션까지. <br>
        하나의 플랫폼에서 모든 업무를 효율적으로 처리하세요.
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center pt-8">
        <button onclick="toggleNovus()" class="bg-white text-dark px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition shadow-xl">
          지금 무료로 시작하기
        </button>
        <button class="bg-surface border border-white/10 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/5 transition flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.752 11.168l-3.197-2.132A1 1 0 0010 9.87v4.263a1 1 0 001.555.832l3.197-2.132a1 1 0 000-1.664z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
          데모 영상 보기
        </button>
      </div>

      <!-- Hero Image / Dashboard Preview -->
      <div class="mt-20 relative mx-auto max-w-5xl group cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleNovus()">
        <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand to-purple-600 rounded-2xl blur opacity-25 group-hover:opacity-50 transition duration-1000"></div>
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519389950473-47ba0277781c?q=80&w=1200" class="relative rounded-2xl border border-white/10 shadow-2xl w-full bg-dark">
        
        <!-- Floating Elements -->
        <div class="absolute -right-8 top-1/2 bg-surface p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 shadow-xl animate-bounce hidden md:block">
           <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
             <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-green-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-green-500">✓</div>
             <div>
               <div class="text-xs text-gray-400">Task Completed</div>
               <div class="text-sm font-bold text-white">Design System Update</div>
             </div>
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Features Grid -->
  <section id="features" class="py-24 bg-surface/50 border-t border-white/5">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-4">왜 Novus인가요?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400">단순한 도구를 넘어, 팀의 성장 엔진이 됩니다.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Feature 1 -->
        <div class="bg-surface p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-brand/50 transition duration-300 group cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleNovus()">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-brand mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition">⚡</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">압도적인 속도</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
            최신 기술 스택으로 구축되어, 로딩 없는 쾌적한 업무 환경을 제공합니다. 
            실시간 동기화로 딜레이 없는 협업이 가능합니다.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Feature 2 -->
        <div class="bg-surface p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-brand/50 transition duration-300 group cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleNovus()">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-purple-400 mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition">🎨</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">직관적인 디자인</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
            복잡한 매뉴얼 없이도 누구나 쉽게 사용할 수 있습니다. 
            업무 흐름을 방해하지 않는 깔끔한 UI를 경험하세요.
          </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Feature 3 -->
        <div class="bg-surface p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-brand/50 transition duration-300 group cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleNovus()">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-blue-400 mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition">🔒</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">강력한 보안</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
            기업급 보안 표준을 준수합니다. 
            데이터 암호화와 2단계 인증으로 소중한 자산을 안전하게 보호합니다.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section id="pricing" class="py-24 px-6 container mx-auto max-w-5xl">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">합리적인 요금제</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400">팀의 규모에 맞는 플랜을 선택하세요.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Starter -->
      <div class="bg-surface border border-white/10 p-8 rounded-2xl">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Starter</h3>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">무료</div>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm mb-8 text-gray-400">
          <li class="flex gap-2 text-white"><span>✓</span> 최대 5명 멤버</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2 text-white"><span>✓</span> 기본 프로젝트 관리</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2 text-white"><span>✓</span> 1GB 저장 공간</li>
        </ul>
        <button onclick="toggleNovus()" class="w-full py-3 bg-white/10 text-white font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition">시작하기</button>
      </div>
      <!-- Pro -->
      <div class="bg-surface border-2 border-brand p-8 rounded-2xl relative transform md:-translate-y-4">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-brand text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase">Most Popular</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Pro</h3>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">₩ 12,000 <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-normal">/월</span></div>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm mb-8 text-gray-400">
          <li class="flex gap-2 text-white"><span>✓</span> 무제한 멤버</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2 text-white"><span>✓</span> 고급 분석 도구</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2 text-white"><span>✓</span> 100GB 저장 공간</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2 text-white"><span>✓</span> 우선 고객 지원</li>
        </ul>
        <button onclick="toggleNovus()" class="w-full py-3 bg-brand text-white font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-brand/90 transition shadow-lg">무료 체험하기</button>
      </div>
      <!-- Enterprise -->
      <div class="bg-surface border border-white/10 p-8 rounded-2xl">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Enterprise</h3>
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">문의</div>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm mb-8 text-gray-400">
          <li class="flex gap-2 text-white"><span>✓</span> 전용 서버 제공</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2 text-white"><span>✓</span> 커스텀 기능 개발</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2 text-white"><span>✓</span> 무제한 저장 공간</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2 text-white"><span>✓</span> 전담 매니저 배정</li>
        </ul>
        <button onclick="toggleNovus()" class="w-full py-3 bg-white/10 text-white font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition">문의하기</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Modal -->
  <div id="novus-modal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/80 backdrop-blur-sm z-[60] hidden flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div class="bg-surface w-full max-w-md p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 relative shadow-2xl">
      <button onclick="toggleNovus()" class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-gray-500 hover:text-white">&times;</button>
      
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Get Started</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">이메일로 간편하게 가입하세요.</p>
      </div>

      <form class="space-y-4" onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('가입 환영 이메일이 발송되었습니다.'); toggleNovus();">
        <input type="email" placeholder="이메일 주소" class="w-full bg-dark border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-3 text-white focus:border-brand outline-none transition">
        <input type="password" placeholder="비밀번호" class="w-full bg-dark border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-3 text-white focus:border-brand outline-none transition">
        
        <button class="w-full bg-brand text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-brand/90 transition mt-2">
          계정 만들기
        </button>
        <p class="text-xs text-center text-gray-500 mt-4">
          계정 생성 시 <a href="#" class="text-brand underline">이용약관</a>에 동의하게 됩니다.
        </p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    function toggleNovus() {
      const modal = document.getElementById('novus-modal');
      if(modal.classList.contains('hidden')) {
        modal.classList.remove('hidden');
      } else {
        modal.classList.add('hidden');
      }
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
